  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个咖啡豆供应链的桑基图，展示从原料到最终交付的流向。核心节点有三个：Beans作为起始原料，Processing代表加工环节，最后到Delivery交付端。另外还有Waste这个分支要处理损耗。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beans",
        "Processing",
        "Delivery",
        "Waste"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我来确认一下流向结构。Beans分出两路对吗？一路去Processing加工，另一路直接去Waste废料？然后Processing之后再到Delivery，Waste那边也有部分能到Delivery？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beans",
        "Processing",
        "Waste",
        "Delivery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但Waste到Delivery不是废料直接交付，是回收再利用的意思。数值上，Beans总量10单位，8份进Processing，2份成为Waste；加工后7份合格交付，Waste里回收1份也能交付。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beans",
        "Processing",
        "Waste",
        "Delivery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先用beta版桑基图把结构搭出来。Beans到Processing画8的宽度，Beans到Waste画2；Processing到Delivery画7，Waste到Delivery画1。这样交付总量是8，符合逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beans",
        "Processing",
        "Waste",
        "Delivery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，Waste到Delivery的流向我觉得需要调整一下表述。不是\"Waste到Delivery\"，应该是回收流重新命名节点？不对，保持节点名也行，但让我想想——其实节点名可以，但数值上Waste总共2份，1份回收交付，剩下1份呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waste",
        "Delivery"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "您是说Waste的2份里只有1份去了Delivery，还有1份没画出来？还是需要补一个最终废弃的节点？目前图上Waste只有出度1，确实不平衡。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waste",
        "Delivery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不用补节点了，实际业务里那1份就是彻底损耗掉了，不出现在交付环节。桑基图可以允许中间节点有损耗，只要Beans的10和最终Delivery的8能对上就行。保持现在这样，Waste节点只有1份流向Delivery，另1份隐式损耗。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beans",
        "Waste",
        "Delivery"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终结构：Beans出度10，Processing收8出7，Waste收2出1，Delivery收8。所有节点和流向都清晰了，beta版桑基图可以正确渲染这个供应链流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Beans",
        "Processing",
